node.text: Our yard is trash. When @meghantnelson and I moved into our house in January, the yard was roughhh. The flippers installed a sprinkler system and it was horrible so basically our entire yard died this year lol Neither of us are landscape designers so we needed help, but hiring firms is so pricey and the lead times are insane. I found @tilly_design and they FaceTimed us about what we liked/wanted. A few weeks later and we had an amazing yard plan with 3D renders and planting instructions. This isn’t sponsored but if you use “Snazzy10” you can save 10% on your plans!
